<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="43" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1121,1225]" pageId="2" pageNumber="43">
<bibRefCitation author="Barroso, G. M." box="[151,336,1121,1147]" pageId="2" pageNumber="43" pagination="1 - 281" refId="ref6519" refString="Barroso, G. M. (1976) Subtribo Baccharidinae Hoffman. Estudo das especies ocorrentes no Brasil. Rodriguesia 28: 1 - 281." type="journal article" year="1976">Barroso (1976)</bibRefCitation>
chose 
<emphasis box="[422,567,1121,1146]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="43">Dusén 2208</emphasis>
at S as the “ 
<typeStatus box="[722,833,1121,1147]" pageId="2" pageNumber="43">holotype</typeStatus>
” of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dusen" authorityYear="1910" box="[886,1082,1121,1146]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Baccharis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="2" pageNumber="43" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="leucocephala">
<emphasis box="[886,1082,1121,1146]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="43">B. leucocephala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This is the only case within 
<taxonomicName authorityName="de Candolle" authorityYear="1836" box="[151,594,1160,1186]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Baccharis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="2" pageNumber="43" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Tarchonanthoides">
<emphasis box="[151,272,1160,1185]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="43">Baccharis</emphasis>
subgen. 
<emphasis box="[381,594,1160,1185]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="43">Tarchonanthoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
where a second-step lectotypification is not required, since Barroso’s choice is in total accordance with the ICBN rules (McNeil 
<emphasis box="[841,900,1199,1224]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="43">et al.</emphasis>
2006).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
